Monkey juice maker:

There is a smart monkey very good at making fruit juice. He has several blenders to work with to prepare juice.

Design a system where a customer can go to a Monkey Blender maker and ask to make juice. 

Advance:
The order or making juice can vary. In one scenario, Monkey wants to make juice in the order of his preferred list of Juice first (which is a blend can be made up of same fruits). 
While in order cases monkey would want to make juice of assorted items.